\mathcal{H}(X) + \sum_{x \in E} p_X(x) (-\sum_{Y \in E} p_{Y|X = x}(y) \log_2 p_{Y|X = x}(y)})\\
 = \mathcal{H}(X) + \mathcal{H}(Y|X)

